{"tid":1520062,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"大劇本已經開始上演！！！","createTime":"2019-08-30T16:48:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-30T17:33:36.000Z","uid":147797,"like":40,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"e4be0690d566faa652a90d218c7a7773fcafbbaa","tid":1520062,"uid":147797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T16:48:17.000Z","msg":"今晚警察比人斬可能係苦肉計！！！<br />\n<br />\n警察傷勢完全唔嚴重，只係流得幾滴血，加上完全無人影到。真相係點無人知！<br />\n<br />\n目的係令到警察聽日更加暴力，製造End Game 氣氛。<br />\n<br />\n我想講<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">其實中共比各位手足更加急</span></span></span>。中共想用苦肉劇加速暴力衝突，快速分化社會各持份者。從而完結今次運動。<br />\n<br />\n你話我係中計黨都係咁話，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">聽日唔好亂衝</span></span>，勇武係必要時先勇武。如果聽日咁快就衝的話，真係完全中計。我明白大家都好嬲，但係要明白<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">呢一場運動係長期抗爭，絕對唔能夠一時三刻消耗所有力量。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求，缺一不可<br />\n光復香港，時代革命<br />\n不受傷，不被捕<br />\n不割席！</span></span>"},{"pid":"a04e6e951806949871190fd53669e0e22f82f7a3","tid":1520062,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T16:48:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Qw3QgZA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQw3QgZA.jpg&h=c3ca146d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=7zzHsEpI0SCc5dEpMOtc2YWZOtE43EI%2FqUWggxD1P9E%3D&h=8ab96f2c\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=7zzHsEpI0SCc5dEpMOtc2YWZOtE43EI%2FqUWggxD1P9E%3D&h=e3b93a80\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwi